=== AGENT SYSTEM ===
- Install command: One-line bash script from /install page
- Language: Bash daemon
- Poll interval: Every 5 minutes
- Functions: Certificate monitoring, auto-renewal, DNS challenge, cert installation
- Status: Visible in /agent-health and /dashboard
- Logs: Available in dashboard
- Restart: systemctl restart sslvault-agent
- Check status: systemctl status sslvault-agent
- Uninstall: systemctl stop sslvault-agent && systemctl disable sslvault-agent

=== DNS PROVIDERS SUPPORTED ===
Cloudflare, Route53, Namecheap, GoDaddy, Porkbun, Dynadot, Name.com, DNSimple, Hover, Gandi, Vultr DNS, DigitalOcean DNS, Linode DNS, Hetzner DNS, and 40+ more. Full list at /dns-providers.

=== CLOUDFLARE SETUP ===
1. Go to Cloudflare dashboard → My Profile → API Tokens
2. Create Token → Use template "Edit zone DNS"
